{"tid":1904522,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"每次開戰個陣連登都會出現呢個問題","createTime":"2020-02-29T16:33:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T19:52:02.000Z","uid":211994,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a21196aeae8784beb16e4bdb7ab2e8b4858246e0","tid":1904522,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:33:03.000Z","msg":"就係亂屌人地係分化散水撚冷氣軍師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">啱嘅說話就係啱，同嗰個人身分無關</span></span><br />\n<br />\n口講話依家打緊仗嘅兒登仔往往最鍾意意氣用事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一係唔理人講咩就開火屌人<br />\n一係話人地條橋唔得，但又唔指出邊度唔得/比其他意見出嚟<br />\n<br />\n叫你走，唔一定要走返屋企，但一定唔係留喺呢度，be water唔一定要go home<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，打陣地係會損傷慘重<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n論裝備唔夠人打、論後果每人最低消費係告你一條暴動罪，纏住你357年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好話咩成班衝埋去一定夠打<br />\n除非你地未等狗列好陣，對方人丁單薄個陣就壓埋去，先會有勝算<br />\n每等多一秒，危險就越大<br />\n<br />\n係呀，見到遮陣好開心呀，覺得大師兄返哂嚟<br />\n<br />\n其實前線根本冇離開過，前線亦唔係為咗燃點你心入面團火而出嚟，大家條命都好重要，唔好要人地用條命提醒你應該意志堅定啲<br />\n<br />\n最後，附上本人整合出嚟嘅<span style=\"color: violet;\">前線手冊</span>，希望幫到咁多位前線手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算依家係抗疫期間，前線手足都一樣咁忙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1893559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1893559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cd519d4d962ecdd10118d6def8654753605fa62f","tid":1904522,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:34:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d564b647314e6967f1e430d805525aea6980db3","tid":1904522,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:35:12.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n手足加油，手足小心，多謝手足<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1813233\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1813233</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"39688ba0124789db690080b079417b7436ac4588","tid":1904522,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:35:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8dcfdb652c3cae557614f0e1d3c64bc5445c2416","tid":1904522,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:35:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3ceff41adb629d1357477f8633cf080a1c2687b","tid":1904522,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:36:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37edaad1f1e8884c1049855054b38a5d195eaaf9","tid":1904522,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T16:43:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3379fdbb00f4bedc47c69732d63724f191f55995","tid":1904522,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T17:22:04.000Z","msg":"啱，唔只開戰，平時都有"},{"pid":"c373278f6d30534ecfeb24350fc16b7c972d2788","tid":1904522,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T17:23:08.000Z","msg":"咁有啲岀名有問題嘅，係值得提醒大家<br />\n但問題係唔可以同自己意見有分歧就屌人身份"},{"pid":"120bbc6caefcfa035aa3cc18f722833a401574ba","tid":1904522,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T17:23:34.000Z","msg":"不過有啲其實係五毛屌人係五毛，賊喊捉賊"},{"pid":"faf289557076d00d32f9fbd271043e71521b75b8","tid":1904522,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T17:24:12.000Z","msg":"咁所以基本上冇內容齋屌身份嘅其實應該無視"},{"pid":"62296d6d2fcd82d756ad7f4818121332660be189","tid":1904522,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T17:24:38.000Z","msg":"睇住live係連登指點江山班冷氣撚我屌曬你地老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1904428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1904428</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a69cac5c087f09ee473e9881021082ea3a4f3076","tid":1904522,"uid":27396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T17:25:24.000Z","msg":"因為冷氣軍師多"},{"pid":"b00124f9e78b2c052c34ceebc14e7bc8dda921e4","tid":1904522,"uid":60583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T17:25:41.000Z","msg":"絕對唔應該回應甚至爭論<br />\n1. 對方三毛，咁當然唔理<br />\n2. 對方自己友，似小朋友扭計，唔好同佢講道理，係要唔理佢，佢自己慢慢會收聲"},{"pid":"7769dcd19e69a92312e2de4c3d4a75cee3a06cf7","tid":1904522,"uid":36483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T17:26:54.000Z","msg":"其實前線根本冇離開過，前線亦唔係為咗燃點你心入面團火而出嚟，大家條命都好重要，唔好要人地用條命提醒你應該意志堅定啲。"},{"pid":"6e52553d068c836dfd4d47152bcf574c9ce9c720","tid":1904522,"uid":272667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T17:27:00.000Z","msg":"手足加油<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！"},{"pid":"38d1ffad39b3c86b90467fae7de37ff4b80a0cc3","tid":1904522,"uid":48582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c373278f6d30534ecfeb24350fc16b7c972d2788","tid":1904522,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T17:23:08.000Z","msg":"咁有啲岀名有問題嘅，係值得提醒大家<br />\n但問題係唔可以同自己意見有分歧就屌人身份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T17:29:06.000Z","msg":"而家一言不合就：你係五毛你係鬼<br />\n咁傾閪咩<br />\n返去打飛機算啦，打到精盡人亡死係最正嘅死法嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5eb80a89a3813d818ca885bb21a41cc0167370","tid":1904522,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T17:32:27.000Z","msg":"根本出左去就唔會睇連登，呢d post 唔知比邊個睇"},{"pid":"4eba007e323618cc53e34e4f4a22381a8ec0ea11","tid":1904522,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T17:39:37.000Z","msg":"好多出去做野嘅人唔睇連登, 我問過啲後生仔16-18歲左右<br />\n佢地都覺得連登啲人好冇聊, 日日嘈埋晒啲冇謂野又唔做實際野<br />\n有人幫佢地做野就打飛機, 正皮射到周地都係 <br />\n結果做野都係同一班人"},{"pid":"97e3f4230bfb2a87bd57215bc989970cc36875df","tid":1904522,"uid":211887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T19:52:02.000Z","msg":"運動雖然好似衰落緊但其實前線一直等緊個機會，我哋照舊會保護大家前提係大家要識玩 唔係得把口屌狗就算 今晚旺角成百幾人比班狗圍係中間就係因為大家唔夠警覺性高"}]}